### Speech to Text

*   [OpenAI Whisper (‚≠ê85k)](https://github.com/openai/whisper) - Whisper is a general-purpose speech recognition model that can be run locally offline. It can transcribe audio from and to multiple languages.

items.title: Awesome Zsh Plugins
items.content_text:
### Plugins / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [aws2 (‚≠ê2)](https://github.com/drgr33n/oh-my-zsh_aws2-plugin) - Provides completion support for version 2 of the [awscli](https://docs.aws.amazon.com/cli/latest/userguide/install-cliv2.html) and a few utilities to manage AWS profiles and display them in the prompt.
*   [firebase (seqi) (‚≠ê9)](https://github.com/Seqi/firebase-zsh) - Display the current working project or project alias when in a Firebase project directory or subdirectory.
*   [k3d (‚≠ê8)](https://github.com/dwaynebradley/k3d-oh-my-zsh-plugin) - Adds aliases and tab completions for [k3d](https://k3d.io/).
*   [oh-my-gpt (‚≠ê1)](https://github.com/vicotrbb/oh-my-gpt) - Provides an easy-to-use interface for interacting with OpenAI's GPT models directly from your terminal. It allows you to send queries, analyze files, and get AI-powered assistance for various tasks.
*   [rose-pine-man (‚≠ê9)](https://github.com/const-void/rose-pine-man) - Colorizes `man` pages.
*   [wsl2-ssh-pageant (‚≠ê1)](https://github.com/antoinemartin/wsl2-ssh-pageant-oh-my-zsh-plugin) - Use your Yubikey stored GPG keys from WSL. This packages the instructions from [wsl2-ssh-pageant repo (‚≠ê369)](https://github.com/BlackReloaded/wsl2-ssh-pageant) as a ZSH plugin.

### Completions / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [completion-sync (‚≠ê16)](https://github.com/BronzeDeer/zsh-completion-sync) - Automatically loads completions added dynamically to `FPATH` or `XDG_DATA_DIRS`.

### Themes / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [rho (‚≠ê0)](https://github.com/andrii-rieznik/rho-zsh-theme) - Minimalist theme. Includes decorators for `git` status, hostname and current directory.
items.content_html:
Plugins / superconsole - Windows-only

  • aws2 (‚≠ê2) - Provides completion support for version 2 of the awscli and a few utilities to manage AWS profiles and display them in the prompt.
  • firebase (seqi) (‚≠ê9) - Display the current working project or project alias when in a Firebase project directory or subdirectory.
  • k3d (‚≠ê8) - Adds aliases and tab completions for k3d.
  • oh-my-gpt (‚≠ê1) - Provides an easy-to-use interface for interacting with OpenAI's GPT models directly from your terminal. It allows you to send queries, analyze files, and get AI-powered assistance for various tasks.
  • rose-pine-man (‚≠ê9) - Colorizes man pages.
  • wsl2-ssh-pageant (‚≠ê1) - Use your Yubikey stored GPG keys from WSL. This packages the instructions from wsl2-ssh-pageant repo (‚≠ê369) as a ZSH plugin.

Completions / superconsole - Windows-only

  • completion-sync (‚≠ê16) - Automatically loads completions added dynamically to FPATH or XDG_DATA_DIRS.

Themes / superconsole - Windows-only

  • rho (‚≠ê0) - Minimalist theme. Includes decorators for git status, hostname and current directory.
